45:44.524 --> 45:47.483
[women laughing]

45:52.010 --> 45:52.793
Psst.

45:53.881 --> 45:54.926
Hey, cutie.

45:56.362 --> 45:59.495
[women laughing]

45:59.539 --> 46:01.454
What are you doing here, Theo?

46:02.847 --> 46:05.284
