and hear me, okay?

46:21.517 --> 46:24.869
-Your mind has been poisoned,
-[disjointed music]

46:27.523 --> 46:29.003
and I know it is
not your fault.

46:29.047 --> 46:31.310
I recognize that, I do.

46:33.703 --> 46:35.967
Your mother and her beliefs,

46:36.010 --> 46:38.708
they were not that of the
apostles, but of her own.

46:40.449 --> 46:41.842
She instilled them into you,

46:41.886 --> 46:43.757
and I need you to see that.

46:44.932 --> 46:46.804
That is why you were
asked to withdraw.

46:49.154 --> 46:52.810
Theo, my mother
taught you how to see,

46:52.853 --> 46:54.550
and you turned on her.

46:54.594 --> 46:56.770
I did not turn
on her, Remy.

46:56.814 --> 46:58.337
-Yes, you did.
-I did not.

47:00.600 --> 47:02.558
She became ill, Remy.

47:03.951 --> 47:05.561
Ill.

47:05.605 --> 47:09.391
And when that happened, she
changed. Her mind changed.

47:12.133 --> 47:14.309
She became barbaric,

47:14.353 --> 47:16.572
