58:40.691 --> 58:43.215
Uh, well, let's see.

58:45.173 --> 58:48.873
Well, I suppose I'm lonely,

58:50.265 --> 58:53.007
just looking to feel
the touch of a woman.

58:56.881 --> 58:58.752
